PRD: Storage Company Landing Page with AI Voice Agent
Project Overview
Build a landing page for Crown Storage with an embedded ElevenLabs conversational AI voice agent. The agent assists prospects by answering questions from a knowledge base, collecting lead information, and scheduling sales consultations via Google Calendar — powered by n8n workflow automations on a self-hosted instance. No backend or database is needed — after each call, n8n sends an email with the collected lead details.
Implementation mandate: The voice agent must be built using the ElevenLabs skills available in the Claude Code project. All n8n workflows must be built using the n8n skills available in the Claude Code project (`n8n-mcp-tools-expert`, `n8n-workflow-patterns`, `n8n-node-configuration`, `n8n-expression-syntax`, `n8n-validation-expert`, `n8n-code-javascript`, `n8n-code-python`). Always consult the relevant skills before implementing any component.
