Agent Tools (ElevenLabs Custom Tools)
The agent needs 3 custom tools configured in ElevenLabs, each calling an n8n webhook.
Tool 1: `check_availability`
Description: Check available time slots for a sales consultation call
Parameters:
Parameter	Type	Required	Description
`preferred_date`	string	No	Customer's preferred date (YYYY-MM-DD). If not provided, check next 3 business days
Webhook URL: `https://n8n.srv983772.hstgr.cloud/webhook/check-availability`
Expected response format:
```json
{
  "available_slots": [
    { "date": "2026-05-04", "time": "10:00 AM", "day": "Monday" },
    { "date": "2026-05-04", "time": "2:00 PM", "day": "Monday" },
    { "date": "2026-05-05", "time": "11:00 AM", "day": "Tuesday" }
  ]
}
```
Tool 2: `book_consultation`
Description: Book a consultation call with a sales representative
Parameters:
Parameter	Type	Required	Description
`customer_name`	string	Yes	Full name of the customer
`customer_phone`	string	Yes	Phone number to call
`date`	string	Yes	Booking date (YYYY-MM-DD)
`time`	string	Yes	Booking time (e.g., "10:00 AM")
`shipment_size`	string	No	Estimated storage size needed
Webhook URL: `https://n8n.srv983772.hstgr.cloud/webhook/book-consultation`
Expected response format:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "booking_id": "BK-20260504-001",
  "confirmed_date": "2026-05-04",
  "confirmed_time": "10:00 AM",
  "message": "Consultation booked successfully"
}
```
Tool 3: `send_lead_email`
Description: Send an email with collected lead information for follow-up
Parameters:
Parameter	Type	Required	Description
`customer_name`	string	Yes	Full name
`customer_phone`	string	Yes	Phone number
`shipment_size`	string	Yes	Estimated storage size
